import React from "react"
import { projects } from "../projects.json"
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'

import {
  Card,
  Box,
  Button,
  Divider,
  Image,
  Stack,
  Set,
  Heading,
  Container,
  Columns,
  Text,
  Paragraph,
  Badge,
} from "bumbag";

const Projects = ({ title, info }) => (
    <Container padding="2rem 1rem">
    <Heading use="h4" marginBottom="major-4">
      Projects
    </Heading>

    <Columns>
    <Columns.Column spread={6}>
      {projects.map(project => (
    <Heading
          use="h4"
          fontWeight="semibold"
          paddingTop="1.5rem"
          paddingBottom="1.5rem"
        >
          {project.title}
        </Heading>
        ))}
    </Columns.Column>
        {/* <Divider /> */}
    </Columns>

    <Columns>
    <Columns.Column spread={6}>
      {projects.map(project => (
    <Paragraph
          use="h4"
          paddingTop="1.5rem"
          paddingBottom="1.5rem"
        >
          {project.info}
        </Paragraph>
        ))}
    </Columns.Column>
    </Columns>
  </Container>
);

export default Projects;
